GET {{baseUrl}}/todo


### new post with the new form of the todo class 
POST {{baseUrl}}/todo HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "clean",
    "item": {
        "item": "clean the bedroom",
        "status": "in progress"
    }
}

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/todo HTTP/1.1

### new post with the new form including the id

POST {{baseUrl}}/todo/list HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

< ./test.json

### 

GET {{baseUrl}}/todo HTTP/1.1


### get using parameters 
GET {{baseUrl}}/todo/3 HTTP/1.1

### example of the same but using 0 
GET {{baseUrl}}/todo/0 HTTP/1.1


### get using query parameters 
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?query=Estudio%20de%20Backend HTTP/1.1


### get using query parameters 2 

GET {{baseUrl}}/search?query=Rutina%20de%20Gimnasio HTTP/1.1


### Using path to make update 

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/todo/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Gym pr",
    "item": {
        "item": "sacar los 150 kg en sentadilla libre el proximo lunes", 
        "status": "Uncompleted"
    }
}

